text: When Moses advenit noster appointed temporis his Dominus spoke cum eum he dictus My Dominus let me look vide Vos, He dictus Vos non vide Me! Look apud ut montis si it stays its locus tunc vos vide Me. Tunc his Dominus manifested montis hoc causa it crumble Moses fell unconscious When he advenit he dictus Vos glorified Ego repent Vos ego the multus convinced believer
